OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1783973917
OL,3,CWhy headteachers are concerned Ofsted
OL,4,Creports could cause more tragedies
OL,6,FITV News' Stacey Foster spoke to 12
OL,7,Fheadteachers about their concerns
OL,8,Fsurrounding Ofsted inspections,
OL,9,Ffollowing the death of Ruth Perry in
OL,10,F2023
OL,12,FWarning: This report contains
OL,13,Freferences to suicide.
OL,15,FEarlier this year, I was contacted by
OL,16,Fa school governor who was worried
OL,17,Fabout a headteacher following a recent
OL,18,FOfsted inspection.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/29
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1783973917
OL,3,CWhy headteachers are concerned Ofsted
OL,4,Creports could cause more tragedies
OL,6,FShe knew that I had previously
OL,7,Freported on the death of Ruth Perry,
OL,8,Ffollowing an Ofsted inspection, which
OL,9,Fa coroner later concluded had
OL,10,Fcontributed to her death.
OL,12,FI agreed to speak to the headteacher.
OL,13,FBut she wasn't ready. It would be
OL,14,Fanother three months before she felt
OL,15,Fable to contact me.
OL,17,FThe full story, I still can't tell,
OL,18,Fbecause she has been warned of the
OL,19,Fconsequences.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/29
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1783973917
OL,3,CWhy headteachers are concerned Ofsted
OL,4,Creports could cause more tragedies
OL,6,FBut I can share this message she sent
OL,7,Fme when I told her we were about to
OL,8,Freport on the issues headteachers are
OL,9,Ffacing under the new Ofsted
OL,10,Finspections that have left her so
OL,11,Fbruised:
OL,13,F"My recent experience of Ofsted was
OL,14,Fincredibly distressing and has been
OL,15,Fseverely detrimental, both personally
OL,16,Fand professionally.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/29
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1783973917
OL,3,CWhy headteachers are concerned Ofsted
OL,4,Creports could cause more tragedies
OL,6,F"Sweeping conjectures based on minutes
OL,7,Fin classrooms and a lack of
OL,8,Fopportunity to evidence and validate
OL,9,Fwhat's typical left me feeling that my
OL,10,Fvast headship experience counted for
OL,11,Fnothing.
OL,13,F"The negative impact upon myself and
OL,14,Fthe staff team is far-reaching. In my
OL,15,Fexperience, no lessons have been
OL,16,Flearnt. If anything, the framework is
OL,17,Fsignificantly worse and the stakes are
OL,18,Feven higher."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/29
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1783973917
OL,3,CWhy headteachers are concerned Ofsted
OL,4,Creports could cause more tragedies
OL,6,FIt was this headteacher's story that
OL,7,Fprompted me to investigate the impact
OL,8,Fof Ofsted's new inspection framework,
OL,9,Fbrought in at the start of 2026.
OL,11,FIt wasn't long before I found others
OL,12,Fwith similar accounts. Two others
OL,13,Fagreed to be interviewed on camera.
OL,14,FOne headteacher spoke to us
OL,15,Fanonymously.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/29
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1783973917
OL,3,CWhy headteachers are concerned Ofsted
OL,4,Creports could cause more tragedies
OL,6,FBefore filming began, he broke down
OL,7,Fseveral times, apologising for being
OL,8,Fupset. I could tell he cared deeply
OL,9,Fabout his school, but the frustration
OL,10,Fof not being able to show inspectors
OL,11,Fthe good work being done was palpable.
OL,13,FHe told me he knew the school needed
OL,14,Fimprovement, but said the way he was
OL,15,Ftreated by inspectors left him feeling
OL,16,Fas Perry did. He described the
OL,17,Finspection as "the worst two days of
OL,18,Fmy entire career... possibly the worst
OL,19,Ftwo days of my adult life".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/29
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1783973917
OL,3,CWhy headteachers are concerned Ofsted
OL,4,Creports could cause more tragedies
OL,6,FHe told me he had experienced suicidal
OL,7,Fthoughts following the inspection.
OL,9,F"I felt that I'd achieved absolutely
OL,10,Fnothing here. Well, I didn't feel that
OL,11,F` I was told that by an inspector in a
OL,12,Fmeeting on my own.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/29
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1783973917
OL,3,CWhy headteachers are concerned Ofsted
OL,4,Creports could cause more tragedies
OL,6,F"And my thoughts on the way home were
OL,7,Fmostly around what I was going to do.
OL,8,FI found myself wondering that for
OL,9,F(headteachers) who didn't go home to a
OL,10,Ffamily in the same way that I was
OL,11,Fgoing to, how easy it would be to take
OL,12,Fone for the team because when there's
OL,13,Fa second death, I suspect that this
OL,14,Fwill have to stop."
OL,26,@qD@ApmqD@Npn
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/29
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
