OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1783973917
OL,3,CWhy headteachers are concerned Ofsted
OL,4,Creports could cause more tragedies
OL,6,FAfter Perry's death, Ofsted carried
OL,7,Fout a consultation exercise called
OL,8,F"The Big Listen". Designed to improve
OL,9,Fheadteacher wellbeing while
OL,10,Fmaintaining standards in schools, the
OL,11,Finspection framework and new report
OL,12,Fcard system were trialled last autumn
OL,13,Fbefore being adopted across England
OL,14,Ffrom January 2026.
OL,16,FAs I write this, I have now been
OL,17,Fcontacted by 12 headteachers who all
OL,18,Fsay the new framework has failed to
OL,19,Faddress concerns around headteacher
OL,20,Fwellbeing.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/29
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1783973917
OL,3,CWhy headteachers are concerned Ofsted
OL,4,Creports could cause more tragedies
OL,6,FA school leader contacted me
OL,7,Fanonymously after an inspection this
OL,8,Fmonth to say that while they were
OL,9,Fpleased with the outcome, the
OL,10,Fexperience was "incredibly challenging
OL,11,Fand far away from something that was
OL,12,Fpromised in light of the death of Ruth
OL,13,FPerry".
OL,15,FThey said: "Staff were sent an email
OL,16,Fat 7.30pm requesting more than 10
OL,17,Fpieces of evidence that inspectors
OL,18,Fwanted for 8.30am the next day.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/29
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1783973917
OL,3,CWhy headteachers are concerned Ofsted
OL,4,Creports could cause more tragedies
OL,6,F"Teachers were in school until 11pm
OL,7,Fthe night before and on day one of the
OL,8,Finspection."
OL,10,FThere were recurring themes in what
OL,11,Fheadteachers told me about the
OL,12,Femotional toll of inspections. Several
OL,13,Fquestioned aspects of the new
OL,14,Fframework itself.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/29
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31212
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1783973917
OL,3,CWhy headteachers are concerned Ofsted
OL,4,Creports could cause more tragedies
OL,6,FSome said linking behaviour and
OL,7,Fattendance was unhelpful when schools
OL,8,Fperformed differently across those
OL,9,Fcategories. Others argued it is
OL,10,Fdifficult for parents to understand
OL,11,Fhow close a school is to achieving the
OL,12,Fnext rating.
OL,14,FOne headteacher told me: "You can be
OL,15,Fone tick away from Strong, but they
OL,16,Fcan't give you a Strong grade, so it
OL,17,Fjust looks like you're Expected
OL,18,FStandard."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/29
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31213
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1783973917
OL,3,CWhy headteachers are concerned Ofsted
OL,4,Creports could cause more tragedies
OL,6,FPerry, the headteacher of Caversham
OL,7,FPrimary School, took her own life in
OL,8,F2023 after learning her school was
OL,9,Flikely to be downgraded following an
OL,10,FOfsted inspection.
OL,12,FA coroner later concluded the
OL,13,Finspection had contributed to her
OL,14,Fdeath and issued a Prevention of
OL,15,FFuture Deaths report to both Ofsted
OL,16,Fand Reading Borough Council.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/29
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31214
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1783973917
OL,3,CWhy headteachers are concerned Ofsted
OL,4,Creports could cause more tragedies
OL,6,FThree years on, Perry's sister, Julia
OL,7,FWaters, remains concerned that not
OL,8,Fenough has been done to address the
OL,9,Fissues identified following her
OL,10,Fsister's death.
OL,12,FShe said: "They should have been doing
OL,13,Feverything in their power to ensure
OL,14,Fthat headteachers are not left feeling
OL,15,Fas Ruth did, and it's very worrying
OL,16,Fand very depressing and actually quite
OL,17,Ffrightening."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/29
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31215
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1783973917
OL,3,CWhy headteachers are concerned Ofsted
OL,4,Creports could cause more tragedies
OL,6,FShe added: "What really worries me is
OL,7,Ffor each person who has contacted me
OL,8,For you, there are probably others who
OL,9,Fhaven't spoken to anyone because they
OL,10,Ffeel ashamed or frightened or bullied
OL,11,Finto not speaking.
OL,13,F"And in a way it's them that I'm more
OL,14,Fworried about."
OL,26,@nD@LOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/29
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
