FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31216
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1783973917
OL,3,CWhy headteachers are concerned Ofsted
OL,4,Creports could cause more tragedies
OL,6,FMiss Waters has spent years lobbying
OL,7,Fministers, Ofsted and
OL,8,Fparliamentarians. She welcomed some
OL,9,Freforms, including the removal of
OL,10,Fsingle-word judgements, but believes
OL,11,Fthat bigger cultural change is still
OL,12,Fneeded.
OL,14,FAmanda Hulme, the headteacher of
OL,15,FClaypool Primary School, wrote to
OL,16,FChief Inspector Sir Martyn Oliver
OL,17,Fafter her Ofsted inspection in
OL,18,FFebruary 2026.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/29
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31217
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1783973917
OL,3,CWhy headteachers are concerned Ofsted
OL,4,Creports could cause more tragedies
OL,6,FShe said it was not a letter of
OL,7,Fcomplaint, but a letter of reflection
OL,8,Fabout what she described as a very
OL,9,Fstressful experience.
OL,11,FMiss Hulme said the inspectors were
OL,12,Fcourteous and professional but that
OL,13,Fshe was frustrated that a set of
OL,14,Fdisappointing exam results resulted in
OL,15,Fthe school receiving a "Needs
OL,16,FAttention" rating for achievement.
OL,18,FThe school then waited more than three
OL,19,Fmonths for its report to be published
OL,20,F` something Miss Hulme told me added
OL,21,Fsignificantly to her stress.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/29
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31218
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1783973917
OL,3,CWhy headteachers are concerned Ofsted
OL,4,Creports could cause more tragedies
OL,6,FShe said. "I feel quite demoralised by
OL,7,Fthe report. It was damaging to my
OL,8,Fhealth at the start of it. I actually
OL,9,Fcontacted three of my closest
OL,10,Fcolleagues and said, if something was
OL,11,Fto happen to me, please will you come
OL,12,Fin to look after my children and my
OL,13,Fstaff during that absence ... that was
OL,14,Fhow worried I was about my own health.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/29
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31219
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1783973917
OL,3,CWhy headteachers are concerned Ofsted
OL,4,Creports could cause more tragedies
OL,6,FShe continued: "My blood pressure
OL,7,Frose, my pulse rate was higher, I
OL,8,Fcouldn't sleep properly, and it's
OL,9,Fbecause you care so much about the
OL,10,Fschool and the children and the staff,
OL,11,Fand I didn't want to let any of them
OL,12,Fdown."
OL,14,FOfsted said it replied to Amanda's
OL,15,Fletter and apologised for the delay.
OL,26,@nD@POU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G19/29
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31220
SC,0020
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1783973917
OL,3,CWhy headteachers are concerned Ofsted
OL,4,Creports could cause more tragedies
OL,6,FGospel Oak Primary School in London
OL,7,Freceived a top report under the new
OL,8,Fsystem. But its headteacher, John
OL,9,FHayes, says he will not go through
OL,10,Fanother inspection after his long
OL,11,Fcareer because of his experiences
OL,12,Funder the new framework.
OL,14,F"During one of the meetings we had
OL,15,Fwith the inspection team, a member of
OL,16,Fmy senior team cried and had to leave
OL,17,Fthe room.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G20/29
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31221
SC,0021
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1783973917
OL,3,CWhy headteachers are concerned Ofsted
OL,4,Creports could cause more tragedies
OL,6,F"I cried too and that caused my deputy
OL,7,Fto call the Ofsted emergency helpline.
OL,8,FIn my professional career I've never
OL,9,Fbeen affected as badly by something as
OL,10,FI was on this occasion.
OL,12,F"And I want to add that we did
OL,13,Fextremely well, but the journey was
OL,14,Ftraumatising and harrowing."
OL,16,FHe added: "At one point I said, 'I'm
OL,17,Fnot OK. I'm terrified. And they had
OL,18,Fnothing to offer me at that point, so
OL,19,Fit does beg the question ` is it just
OL,20,Fpiecemeal? Are they just asking
OL,21,Fbecause they are told to ask?"
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G21/29
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31222
SC,0022
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1783973917
OL,3,CWhy headteachers are concerned Ofsted
OL,4,Creports could cause more tragedies
OL,6,FOfsted said it received two calls to
OL,7,Fthe emergency wellbeing line during
OL,8,FGospel Oak's inspection. Inspectors
OL,9,Foffered to pause the process, which
OL,10,Fwas declined. Ofsted has since
OL,11,Fapologised.
OL,13,FThe inspectorate says it has
OL,14,Fintroduced significant changes,
OL,15,Fincluding replacing headline
OL,16,Fjudgements with report cards and
OL,17,Fintroducing wellbeing measures for
OL,18,Finspections.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G22/29
