PN,31225
SC,0025
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1783973917
OL,3,CWhy headteachers are concerned Ofsted
OL,4,Creports could cause more tragedies
OL,6,FA Department for Education
OL,7,Fspokesperson said: "A robust
OL,8,Finspection system is essential to help
OL,9,Fevery child achieve and thrive `
OL,10,FOfsted's new report cards give parents
OL,11,Fand teachers a clearer, more
OL,12,Ftransparent picture of what's working
OL,13,Fand where change is needed.
OL,15,F"We're continuing to work closely with
OL,16,FOfsted and school leaders to make sure
OL,17,Finspections are collaborative,
OL,18,Fconstructive and fair.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G25/29
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
