FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31226
SC,0026
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1783973917
OL,3,CWhy headteachers are concerned Ofsted
OL,4,Creports could cause more tragedies
OL,6,F"Great headteachers transform schools
OL,7,F` that's why we're backing them with
OL,8,Fmentoring, coaching and wellbeing
OL,9,Fsupport through our Excellence in
OL,10,FLeadership offer, keeping the best
OL,11,Fheads where they belong: in schools."
OL,13,FEvery headteacher I spoke to supported
OL,14,Faccountability. Several explicitly
OL,15,Ftold me they believed inspections were
OL,16,Fnecessary.
OL,18,FOne headteacher told me: "I wouldn't
OL,19,Fwant to work in a system where they
OL,20,Fdidn't (have inspections).
OL,26,@|D@Hpm|D@Ypn
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G26/29
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31227
SC,0027
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1783973917
OL,3,CWhy headteachers are concerned Ofsted
OL,4,Creports could cause more tragedies
OL,6,F"What I want is for inspectors to be
OL,7,Faccountable ... But inspectors must
OL,8,Falso be held to account for how they
OL,9,Fconduct themselves and how they
OL,10,Fconduct an inspection."
OL,12,FOf course, these 12 headteachers do
OL,13,Fnot represent every school leader's
OL,14,Fexperience of the new framework. More
OL,15,Fthan 1,400 schools have been inspected
OL,16,Fsince January, and many leaders report
OL,17,Fpositive experiences.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G27/29
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
