OL,3,CWhy headteachers are concerned Ofsted
OL,4,Creports could cause more tragedies
OL,6,FNew research from the campaign group
OL,7,F"The Alternative Big Listen", fronted
OL,8,Fby two former senior Ofsted Inspectors
OL,9,Fasked 100 schools for their views on
OL,10,Fthe new inspection framework.
OL,12,FOf those responding to the
OL,13,Fquestionnaire, almost 70% expressed
OL,14,Fnegative views on Ofsted's impact on
OL,15,Fheadteachers' well-being, including
OL,16,Feight who stated that they had decided
OL,17,Fto retire before another Ofsted
OL,18,Finspection.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G28/29
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
